{"thag5.12:0.1":"Theragatha 5.12 ","thag5.12:0.2":"Pancakanipata ","thag5.12:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag5.12:0.4":"Kosiyattheragatha ","thag5.12:1.1":"“Yo ve garunam vacanannu dhiro, ","thag5.12:1.2":"Vase ca tamhi janayetha pemam; ","thag5.12:1.3":"So bhattima nama ca hoti pandito, ","thag5.12:1.4":"Natva ca dhammesu visesi assa. ","thag5.12:2.1":"Yam apada uppatita ulara, ","thag5.12:2.2":"Nakkhambhayante patisankhayantam; ","thag5.12:2.3":"So thamava nama ca hoti pandito, ","thag5.12:2.4":"Natva ca dhammesu visesi assa. ","thag5.12:3.1":"Yo ve samuddova thito anejo, ","thag5.12:3.2":"Gambhirapanno nipunatthadassi; ","thag5.12:3.3":"Asamhariyo nama ca hoti pandito, ","thag5.12:3.4":"Natva ca dhammesu visesi assa. ","thag5.12:4.1":"Bahussuto dhammadharo ca hoti, ","thag5.12:4.2":"Dhammassa hoti anudhammacari; ","thag5.12:4.3":"So tadiso nama ca hoti pandito, ","thag5.12:4.4":"Natva ca dhammesu visesi assa. ","thag5.12:5.1":"Atthanca yo janati bhasitassa, ","thag5.12:5.2":"Atthanca natvana tatha karoti; ","thag5.12:5.3":"Atthantaro nama sa hoti pandito, ","thag5.12:5.4":"Natva ca dhammesu visesi assa”ti. ","thag5.12:5.5":"… Kosiyo thero …. ","thag5.12:5.6":"Pancakanipato nitthito. ","thag5.12:6.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag5.12:6.1":"Rajadatto subhuto ca, ","thag5.12:6.2":"girimanandasumana; ","thag5.12:6.3":"Vaddho ca kassapo thero, ","thag5.12:6.4":"gayakassapavakkali. ","thag5.12:7.1":"Vijito yasadatto ca, ","thag5.12:7.2":"sono kosiyasavhayo; ","thag5.12:7.3":"Satthi ca panca gathayo, ","thag5.12:7.4":"thera ca ettha dvadasati. "}